---
import Header from "../components/company/CompanyHeader.astro";
import Footer from "../components/company/CompanyFooter.astro";

const EFFECTIVE_DATE = "September 21, 2025";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>LEGAL CENTER | ASHAK STUDIOS</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@300;400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
      :root {
        --color-bg: #000000;
        --color-text: #FFFFFF;
        --color-muted: #888888;
        --color-border: #333333;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .main-content {
        padding: 160px 40px 100px;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(60px, 10vw, 120px);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: -4px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .section-label {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 300;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        margin-bottom: 80px;
        display: block;
      }

      /* --- TOC --- */
      .toc {
        display: flex;
        gap: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 80px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); /* BU KALDI: Öbür divider */
        padding-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .toc-link {
        color: var(--color-text);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        transition: opacity 0.3s;
      }

      .toc-link:hover { opacity: 0.5; }

      /* --- LEGAL ITEMS --- */
      .legal-section {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .legal-card {
        /* Buralardaki border-top'u komple sildik! Artık aralarda çizgi yok */
        padding: 100px 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
        gap: 60px;
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
      }

      .doc-title {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .meta-scope {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        margin-top: 20px;
        display: block;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      code {
        background: #111;
        color: #FFF;
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-family: monospace;
      }

      /* --- TEXT CONTENT --- */
      .legal-body h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #FFF;
        margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .legal-body h3:not(:first-child) {
        margin-top: 40px;
      }

      .legal-body p, .legal-body li {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .legal-body ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .legal-body a {
        color: #FFF;
        text-decoration: underline;
        transition: opacity 0.3s;
      }

      .legal-body a:hover { opacity: 0.6; }

      @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .legal-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding: 60px 0; }
        .hero-title { letter-spacing: -2px; }
        .main-content { padding: 120px 20px 60px; }
        .toc { gap: 20px; overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 15px; }
        .toc-link { white-space: nowrap; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <Header />

    <main class="main-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">LEGAL<br/>CENTER.</h1>
      <span class="section-label">Effective: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</span>

      <nav class="toc">
        <a href="#privacy" class="toc-link">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="#terms" class="toc-link">Terms of Use</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="legal-section">
        
        <article id="privacy" class="legal-card">
          <div class="legal-meta">
            <h2 class="doc-title">Privacy Policy</h2>
            <div class="meta-scope">
              <strong>Scope:</strong> This policy applies to the promotional website located at <code>ashak.co</code>. It does not cover our apps or app stores.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-body">
            <h3>1) Summary</h3>
            <p>
              This Site is a simple, read‑only company presentation. We do not run sign‑ups, comments, contact forms, or user accounts. We do not ask you for your name, email address, phone number, payment details, or any similar personal information on this Site.
            </p>

            <h3>2) What We Collect</h3>
            <p>
              <strong>Nothing that identifies you personally.</strong> We do not use first‑party cookies, analytics beacons, fingerprinting, or tracking pixels on this Site. We do not combine, sell, or share any personal data.
            </p>

            <h3>3) Hosting & Basic Technical Logs</h3>
            <p>
              Our hosting provider may process minimal, short‑lived technical logs (e.g., IP address and user‑agent) solely to deliver the Site securely and for anti‑abuse and reliability purposes. We do not use these logs to identify you, and we do not merge them with any other data.
            </p>

            <h3>4) Third‑Party Links</h3>
            <p>
              The Site may link to third‑party pages (e.g., App Store / Google Play, social profiles). When you follow those links, their privacy policies apply.
            </p>

            <h3>5) Children</h3>
            <p>
              The Site is a general‑audience informational page. It does not collect personal information from anyone, including children.
            </p>

            <h3>6) Changes</h3>
            <p>
              If we materially change this policy, we will update the Effective Date above. Your continued use of the Site after changes means you accept the updated policy.
            </p>

            <h3>7) Contact</h3>
            <p>
              Questions? Email <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article id="terms" class="legal-card">
          <div class="legal-meta">
            <h2 class="doc-title">Terms of Use</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-body">
            <h3>1) About These Terms</h3>
            <p>
              These Terms govern your access to and use of this Site. By visiting or using the Site, you agree to these Terms.
            </p>

            <h3>2) Informational Website Only</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>No account creation, sign‑in, or user‑generated content features exist on this Site.</li>
              <li>We provide company and product information and outbound links only.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>3) Acceptable Use</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Do not interfere with the Site’s operation or security.</li>
              <li>Do not attempt to scrape at a rate that degrades service or violates applicable laws.</li>
              <li>Do not use the Site in a way that infringes intellectual property or privacy rights.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>4) Intellectual Property</h3>
            <p>
              Unless otherwise noted, the Site’s text, graphics, logos, and other materials are owned by Ashak Studios or licensed to us and are protected by applicable laws. You may view the Site for personal, non‑commercial use. Any other use requires prior written permission.
            </p>

            <h3>5) Links to Third Parties</h3>
            <p>
              Outbound links (e.g., app stores, social media) are provided for convenience. We are not responsible for their content, availability, or policies.
            </p>

            <h3>6) Disclaimer & Limitation of Liability</h3>
            <p>
              The Site is provided “as is” and “as available” without warranties of any kind. To the maximum extent permitted by law, we disclaim all warranties and will not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from or relating to your use of the Site.
            </p>

            <h3>7) Changes</h3>
            <p>
              We may update or discontinue the Site or these Terms at any time. If we update these Terms, the Effective Date above will change.
            </p>

            <h3>8) Contact</h3>
            <p>
              For any questions about these Terms, contact <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>